name: BabeAnoid
overview: BabeAnoid is a feature-packed breakout clone for the Commodore Amiga. It sports 5 stages, with a total of 45 levels, 7 ball modes, 30 types of bonus blocks, 200 overall block types, 5 enemy types, an equipment store, and even a bonus game. Despite the title, it doesn't feature any adult content, beyond a bikini-clad woman on the menu screen.
